name: Thrice The Alchemy Index Vinyl Box Set
description:
The Alchemy Index is a two-volume collection comprised of four EPs, each devoted to one of the essential elements in nature—fire, water, air and earth—with each EP sonically and thematically tailored to evoke the atmosphere inherent in its corresponding element.

Each of the 4 EP’s will be pressed on 10” colored vinyl -the Fire EP is red, Water is blue, Earth is brown and Air is on clear vinyl. The discs are inside a hand-bound hardcover book complete with lyrics, liner notes and commentary from the band. Limited to only 3000 pressings.

Track Listing:

Vol I: Fire

   1. Firebreather
   2. The Messenger
   3. Backdraft
   4. The Arsonist
   5. Burn the Fleet
   6. The Flame Deluge

Vol II: Water

   1. Digital Sea
   2. Open Water
   3. Lost Continent
   4. Night Diving
   5. The Whaler
   6. Kings Upon the Main

Vol III: Air

   1. Broken Lungs
   2. The Sky Is Falling
   3. A Song for Milly Michaelson
   4. Daedalus
   5. As the Crow Flies
   6. Silver Wings

Vol IV: Earth

   1. Moving Mountains
   2. Digging My Own Grave
   3. The Earth Isn't Humming (Frodus cover) 
   4. The Lion and the Wolf
   5. Come All You Weary
   6. Child of Dust
